<paragraph id="IFRS01_IG61" base="F7284294" principles="no"><paranum>IG61</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="IG61"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS01_P1073">An entity that adopts the fair value model in <xref id="IFRS01_X1371" base="F15829435" href="../ias40/IAS40_TOC0001.dita#IAS40_TOC0001">IAS 40</xref>  measures its investment property at fair value at the date of transition to IFRSs.  The transitional requirements of IAS 40 do not apply (<xref id="IFRS01_X1375" base="F15829497" href="IFRS01_9.dita#IFRS01_9">paragraph 9</xref> of the IFRS).</p></body></paragraph>